/-!
# Linearized Einstein 00-Equation

Derives the 00-component of Einstein equations in Newtonian gauge:
G_00 = κ T_00 → ∇²Φ = 4πG(ρ + ρ_ψ)
-/

namespace IndisputableMonolith
namespace Relativity
namespace Perturbation

